OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775999464
OL,3,CMan convicted of sharing 'extremely
OL,4,Cgraphic' terrorist videos on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FA 23 year old man from Gillingham in
OL,8,FKent has been found guilty of sharing
OL,9,F"extremely graphic" terrorist videos
OL,10,Fonline, according to Counter Terrorism
OL,11,FPolicing South East (CTPSE).
OL,13,FMohammad Malik, of Burnt Oak Terrace,
OL,14,Fwas convicted following a four-week
OL,15,Ftrial at Winchester Crown Court of two
OL,16,Fcounts of disseminating a terrorist
OL,17,Fpublication and two charges of
OL,18,Fexpression of support for a proscribed
OL,19,Forganisation.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@SO]
