PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775999464
OL,3,CMan convicted of sharing 'extremely
OL,4,Cgraphic' terrorist videos on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FHe was acquitted of a count of
OL,8,Fpossession of a terrorist publication
OL,9,Fand a further charge of disseminating
OL,10,Fa terrorist publication.
OL,12,FCTPSE said it had launched an
OL,13,Finvestigation when it was alerted to
OL,14,FMalik sharing footage of several
OL,15,FIslamist groups over different social
OL,16,Fmedia platforms.
OL,18,FThe force raided his home on January
OL,19,F14 2025 and seized a phone, a computer
OL,20,Fand hard drives, swords, knives and a
OL,21,Fhomemade Daesh flag.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
