FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775999464
OL,3,CMan convicted of sharing 'extremely
OL,4,Cgraphic' terrorist videos on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FDetective Chief Superintendent Claire
OL,8,FFinlay, head of CTPSE said "Malik
OL,9,Fshared a number of extremely graphic
OL,10,Fvideos online including some content
OL,11,Fproduced by the media wing of Daesh.
OL,13,FThe videos, some of which he edited
OL,14,Fhimself, glorified the actions of
OL,15,Fproscribed terrorist groups and
OL,16,Fterrorist attacks.
OL,18,FSome of the content he shared was anti-
OL,19,FSemitic and some videos featured
OL,20,Ffootage of executions and beheadings.
OL,26,@pD@\OU
