PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1775999464
OL,3,CMan convicted of sharing 'extremely
OL,4,Cgraphic' terrorist videos on social
OL,5,Cmedia
OL,7,FThese were shared with his followers
OL,8,Fonline and could have encouraged or
OL,9,Fassisted others to become involved in
OL,10,Facts of terrorism.
OL,12,FThe harm from such cases cannot be
OL,13,Funderestimated, particularly towards
OL,14,Fthose vulnerable to radicalisation.
OL,16,FPlease stay vigilant when you are
OL,17,Fonline and be alert to anyone around
OL,18,Fyou whose behaviour may have changed
OL,19,For who may be getting drawn into
OL,20,Fviewing or sharing extreme content."
OL,26,@|D@dO]
